  <brief_title>Comparison of Different Low Volume Solutions Prior to Colonoscopy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Efficiency and Tolerance of Sodium Picosulphate/ Magnesium Citrate, Polyethylene Glycol/Ascorbate and Oral Sulfate Solution Before Colonoscopy</official_title>
