  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Study evaluates the head -to-head efficacy and tolerability of low volume preparations prior
      to colonoscopy
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Aim of the study: To compare the efficacy and tolerance of sodium picosulphate/magnesium
      citrate, polyethylene glycol/ascorbic acid and oral sulfate formula in a single or split dose
      regimen prior to colonoscopy
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
